;========================================================
;
; In an abandoned house in the ghost town of Tanba, some strange demonic paintings are reported 
; to appear during the darkest nights. Since many people where violently murdered in this place, 
; there is no doubt for anybody that this phenomenon is the work of the ghosts left here.
;
; Stage from the game Samurai Shodown V by SNK-Playmore.
;
; M.U.G.E.N. adaptation by R.o.q.u.e.
;
; Special thanks to :
;  - SNK-Playmore for the Samurai Shodown series
;  - Mr K, for WinKawaks
;  - Corel, for Paint Shop Pro
;  - Sés, for M.C.M.
;  - Christophe and Winane, for SFFExtract
;  - Elecbyte, for Sprmaker
;
; For more M.U.G.E.N. material, visit the website : http://alice-games.org
;
; Note : actually this stage is an alternate background that would appear when a fighter enters 
; his Rage Explosion mode in the Abandoned House stage. Since I liked the background, I decided 
; to make it into an independent stage.
;
;========================================================


